Dukansu suna ɗauke da hukuncin kisa, kamar yadda aka rubuta a cikin takardar kotu.
Bayan 'yan makonni bayan da aka kama Saipov, babban mai gabatar da kara na gwamnati ya gurfanar da shi a kan wasu laifuka 22 da suka hada da laifuka takwas na cin hanci da rashawa don tallafawa masu fashi, wanda masu aikata laifuka suka yi amfani da shi a lokuta da dama, da kuma gudanar da cin hanci da rashawa da kuma lalata motoci.
Gidan ya bukaci "tsarin da gwaji mai tsanani", in ji masu sukar, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata "a cikin zalunci, zalunci da mugunta".
Sanarwar ta sirri ta "raunata, wahala, da rashin ga dangi da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Galle Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Digi Pagnucco".
