"Shin tana kuka ne?"
Amurka da China za su iya amfani da dabarun yaki da Beijing
Babban mahimmancin yakin tsakanin Amurka da China ya yi yawa, kuma yayin da yakin ya yi yawa, bambancin da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu zai iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi gargadin farko a farkon wannan shekarar kan batun karɓar takunkumin da China ta yi wa masana'antun hasken rana da na karfe da na shuka.
A cikin wannan makon, an kara karuwar haraji kan kayayyakin da ke da darajar dala biliyan 200 (£150 biliyan), wanda ya kai kashi 50 cikin 100 na kayayyakin da Amurka ke shigowa da su daga China.
Beijing tana biyan ta a kowane lokaci ta hanyar tsabar kudi, kuma a halin yanzu tana ba da dala biliyan 60 na tsabar kudi ga Amurka.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta yi daidai da Amurka, wadda ita ce kasa ta biyu mafi karfin tattalin arziki a duniya, ba za ta iya samun ci gaba ba nan gaba.
Yin biyayya ga Washington don samun nasara yana nufin yin watsi da mu, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping.
Amma, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi amfani da katin da ta yi a dā yadda ya dace, hakan zai sa Amurka ta yi amfani da takunkunta don ta rage dogaro da take da shi a kan sauran ƙasashen biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa Washington ko Beijing za su iya yanke shawara cikin hanzari, zai iya haifar da yanayin da za a iya fara juyin juya halin tattalin arziki a cikin kowace ƙasa wanda ya fi muni fiye da yadda masu kallo suka saba gani", in ji Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike da kuma mai ba da shawara kan Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Harkokin Tsaron Amurka.
'Suriya a shirye take' don sake dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar, in ji wakilin wata kasa
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta ba da damar 'yan gudun hijirar su koma gidajensu, kuma ta ba da damar sake gina kasar da ta yi shekaru bakwai ana yaki.
Yayin da yake jawabi ga Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin ƙasar ya yi kyau.
"A yanzu, a cikin ƙasa mai kyau, godiya ta fi ƙarfin da aka samu a cikin gwagwarmaya da zuciya", in ji shi.
Gwamnati ta ci gaba da yin gyare-gyare a yankunan da masu bincike suka lalata don su sake dawo da yanayin da ya dace.
A halin yanzu, akwai cikakkiyar yanayin da 'yan gudun hijirar ke komawa ƙasarsu saboda matsalolin tattalin arziki da ke shafar rayuwarsu da kuma aikin su.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Siriya miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun bayan da aka fara yaki a kasar a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida kuma suna zama a wuraren da ake bukatar taimako sosai.
Al-Moualem ya ce al'ummar Syria za su iya taimakawa wajen sake gina wuraren da aka lalata.
Amma ya nanata cewa ba za su karɓi wani taimako daga ƙasashen da suka goyi bayan wannan tsanantawa ba.
Turai zuwa Turai lashe gasar Ryder a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 bayan ta doke Amurka da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a wasan karshe da aka yi a Le Golf National a wajen birnin Paris na Faransa.
Amurkawa sun rasa gasar cin kofin Turai a karo na shida a jere a kasa kuma ba su taba lashe kofin Ryder ba a Turai tun daga shekarar 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambinta na farko a gasar cin kofin duniya, bayan da kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ya samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata don doke Amurka.
<seg id="5">Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi fama da matsanancin hali a gasar, ya harba bakinsa a rami na 3-16 inda ya yi wasa da Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya haskaka a cikin dukkan tsalle-tsalle, ya zama 1 daga cikin 'yan wasan 4 da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Jordan Spieth na Amurka ya sha kashi a wasan 5&4 da Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark, wanda shi ne dan wasan da ya fi kowa tsada a Turai.
Babban zakara a duniya, Edo Johnson, ya fadi 2 da 1 a kan Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda ya yi wasa a gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe.
A cikin gwagwarmaya da takwas Ryder Cup, Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama zakara tare da Turai mai nasara 25.5 sau.
"Ba na kuka amma ba zan iya taimakawa a yau ba.
Wannan shekara ta kasance mai wuya.
Na gode wa Allah da ya sa na gaskata da abin da ya gaya mini.
Na yi farin ciki sosai, na yi farin ciki da na sake samun wannan ƙoƙon.
"Wannan shi ne karo na farko da na taba yi a gasar zakarun Turai, kuma ina farin ciki da na taimaka", in ji Garcia bayan ya lashe gasar zakarun Turai.
Ya mika wannan haske ga abokin hamayyarsa John Ram wanda ya saukar da gwarzon dan wasan golf na Amurka Tiger Woods 2&1 a wasan daya a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Ina alfahari da na doke Tiger Woods, kuma na yi girma ina kallon mutumin".
Ya yi hasarar sau hudu a Faransa kuma yana da tarihin 13-21-3 a cikin Ryder Cup.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki daga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na kowane lokaci, wanda ya lashe manyan lakabi 14 kuma ya kasance na biyu kawai ga Jack Nicklaus.
Kungiyar Amurka ta yi gwagwarmaya sosai a karshen mako don neman manyan masu wasa tare da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasan golf mai kyau a duk lokacin gasar.
Wani sojan Amirka mai suna Jim Furyk ya ce bayan wani babban wasan kwaikwayo da sojojinsa suka yi: "Ina farin ciki da waɗannan samari da suka yi yaƙi.
A safiyar yau, mun tashi zuwa Turai.
Mun yi bincike sosai.
Na gode wa Thomas.
Shi babban ma'aikacin jirgin ruwa ne.
Dukan 'yan wasansa 12 sun yi wasa mai kyau.
Za mu yi aiki tare, zan yi aiki tare da PGA da Amurka da kuma kwamitin Ryder Cup kuma za mu ci gaba.
Waɗannan samari goma sha biyu da nake ƙauna sosai ne suka zama shugabanmu.
Ya kamata ka nuna cewa kana da bangaskiya.
An ruɗe mu".
Sabuntawar Red Sea: An sa ido kan Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobi ta Florida ya nuna cewa yawan Red Tide a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
<seg id="3">Kamar yadda FWC ta ce, ana ba da rahoton yanayin gas a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma yankuna masu yawa - wanda ke nuna rashin hangen nesa.
Akwai babban ruwan sama mai suna Red Tide wanda ke da nisan mil 80 daga arewacin Pinella zuwa kudu da Lee.
Ana iya samun ƙwayoyin cuta a kusan nisan mil 10 a cikin Hillsborough County, amma a wurare da yawa a cikin 'yan makonni da suka gabata.
An kuma yi bincike a kan Red Tide a yankin Pasco.
A cikin makon da ya gabata an bayar da rahoton cewa an yi tawaye da nau'ikan da ke faruwa a cikin ko kusa da Pinellas County, a cikin manyan filayen filayen Hillsborough County, zuwa manyan filayen filayen filayen Manatee County, zuwa manyan filayen filayen filayen Sarasota County, zuwa manyan filayen filayen Charlotte County, da kuma zuwa ƙananan filayen filayen Collier County.
Har ila yau, an yi magana a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma yawan wuraren da ake kira collier.
Ba a samu rahoton wani cutar rashin numfashi ba a yankin Arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
